Package no.uio.duo

Class Summary
CristinBundleVersioningStrategy This versioning strategy does nothing, it simply returns leaving all the bundles alone, as the versioning will be handled by the ORE ingester
CristinIngestFilter Implementation of the IngestFilter which determines whether the incoming harvest record should be accepted or not
CristinIngestionWorkflow Implementation of the Harveter's IngestionWorkflow, providing hooks for the OAI-PMH harvesting features.
CristinMetadataRemover Implementation of the MetadataRemover interface, which allows us to selectively clear old metadata before the item is updated
CristinOAIDCCrosswalk A crosswalk to be used with the CRISTIN oai_dc document.
CristinOREImporter Importer which implements both the standard DSpace IngestionCrosswalk and the more advanced OAIConfigurableCrosswalk.
DeduplicateCristinIds Command line script to detect when two cristin IDs are present in the dataset and to output a human readable list of the matches.
DSpace18FixedDispatcher A near-clone of the BasicDispatcher with some cunning-ness/hackery built in to circumvent the concurrent modification exceptions the basicdispatcher is prone to.
DuoConstants  
DuoEmbargoLifter Implemetation of the EmbargoLifter, which ensures that Duo polices are set as required
DuoEntryDisseminator Implementation of the SwordEntryDisseminator which can provide the embedded metadata for StudentWeb alongside a Dublin Core version of the metadata
DuoInstallConsumer Event consumer for Duo which responds to Item Installs.
DuoPolicyManager Class to manage item access policies (and bundles and bitstreams in those items)
FileManager Class to provide file and bundle management utilities for the Duo module
FSBagItIngester Sword Content Ingester to deal with the BagIt format used by the StudentWeb/FS integration
FSEntryIngester Implementation of the SwordEntryIngester interface which takes the FS metadata as embedded in an atom entry and adds it to an existing object
FSPackager Deprecated.
IncomingBitstream Entity class to represent a bitstream being retrieved from Cristin
MetadataManager Class for providing utilities for Metadata management in the Duo module
URNGenerator Command line script to enhance the metadata of an item with a URN retrieved from the National Library and the urls of all the bitstreams associated with an item
WorkflowManagerWrapper Wraper class providing an abstraction over the DSpace workflow manager.
XmlUIBitstreamReorder Processing action to handle the change of bitstream orders in the customisable workflow
XmlUIBitstreamReorderUI XMLUI Action to provide a bitstream reorder UI
XmlUICollectionAssignment Processing action to handle the assignment of an item to multiple collections
XmlUICollectionAssignmentUI XMLUI Action to provide a Collection assignment workflow stage
XmlUICollectionAssignmentUI.TreeNode Private class to represent the tree structure of communities & collections.
